{
  "id": "adv_event_2307_01_02",
  "title": "ボコるしか\nない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-reia001.m4a",
      "text": "『恋々Poison』の麗亜です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm Lea from 'Lovesick Poison'.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.7117007256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうぞよろしくお願いいたします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a pleasure to meet you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6,
      "endTime": 5.9400001526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "夏希",
      "speakerNameEn": "Natsuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-natsuki001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらにいるのが、華乃\n私は同じく『恋々Poison』の夏希です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This here is Kano‚\nand I'm Natsuki‚ also from 'Lovesick Poison'.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1333333333,
      "endTime": 11.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "初めまして、今回はよろしくお願いいたします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you. We're looking forward to working with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8333334606,
      "endTime": 15.2476191681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.452018118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXのfranです\nいい番組になるよう、精一杯やらせていただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fran from ⅢX.\nWe'll do our best to make this a great show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.452018118,
      "endTime": 21.472880029800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6772789797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob4",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-producer001.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、番組の内容をご説明いたしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ let me explain the program's content.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6772789797,
      "endTime": 24.777278931999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob4",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-producer002.m4a",
      "text": "基本的には、『恋々Poison』と\nスリクスのみなさんで、三番勝負をしていただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Basically‚ 'Lovesick Poison' and\nⅢX will compete in three challenges.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9772789797,
      "endTime": 30.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2439470452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "一人ずつ、それぞれ別のゲームで勝負ってことですよね\n台本はどんな感じになるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we'll each compete in different games‚ right?\nHow's the script going to look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2439470452,
      "endTime": 37.6064413232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob4",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-producer003.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームの種目だけ、こちらで指定させていただきますが\n後はみなさん次第です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll only specify the games.\nThe rest is up to you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8108402731,
      "endTime": 43.0108403684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.2108402731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob4",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-producer004.m4a",
      "text": "この番組はガチンコ対決がウリですからね\nスリクスのみなさんも、本気でお願いしますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This show is all about genuine competition.\nSo please‚ give it your all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2108402731,
      "endTime": 49.250840521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4441736064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ、望むところです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's exactly what we want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4441736064,
      "endTime": 52.6015659175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8059648675
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob4",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob4.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-producer005.m4a",
      "text": "当日は、砂浜の特設セットから生放送の予定です\nスリクスのみなさんにお願いしたいのは、まず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live broadcast will be from a special set on the beach.\nFor now‚ let's proceed as planned for ⅢX…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8059648675,
      "endTime": 60.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……それでは、そのような感じで進めていただければ\n当日まで、よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright then‚ let's move forward with that.\nLooking forward to working with you until the day of the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5726282282,
      "endTime": 68.5184559984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.7228549483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（『恋々Poison』もちゃんとした人達だよな）\n（kanaさんが言うようには、あまり見えないけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（'Lovesick Poison' seems like a decent group.）\n（They don't seem as bad as kana-san said.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7228549483,
      "endTime": 75.5204965117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7248954616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-reia002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ\nスリクスのみなさんにお渡ししたいものがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ by the way‚\nwe have something we'd like to give to the members of ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7248954616,
      "endTime": 80.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.0915717922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-reia003.m4a",
      "text": "うちで出してるマスカラなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a mascara from our brand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0915717922,
      "endTime": 87.4266738735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ウォータープルーフなので、海の撮影でもぜひ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's waterproof‚ so it's perfect for beach shoots!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7,
      "endTime": 87.73333333330001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9582399848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "夏希",
      "speakerNameEn": "Natsuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-hanano001.m4a",
      "text": "この子、コスメのプロデュースもやってるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This girl also produces cosmetics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9582399848,
      "endTime": 91.3115682605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.5249015652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、凄いわね\nでも、いろいろと大変なことも多いでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ that's impressive.\nBut it must be tough at times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5249015652,
      "endTime": 97.6666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-reia004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、おかげさまで、どこのお店でも売り切れ続出で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thanks to everyone‚ it's sold out everywhere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8209760828,
      "endTime": 106.6552160425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.8209760828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "早く追加分をくれって言われて、大変なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're constantly asked for more stock‚ which is a challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8666666667,
      "endTime": 106.920968644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "……へえ、頑張ってるのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see‚ you're working hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1209684533,
      "endTime": 110.094006936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2984058859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-reia005.m4a",
      "text": "アパレルメーカーとのコラボの話もあるんです\n良ければ、franさんのブランドともコラボ出来たら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're also talking about a collaboration with an apparel brand.\nIf you're interested‚ we could collaborate with your brand too‚ fran-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2984058859,
      "endTime": 118.47174029370001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.6650735698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "夏希",
      "speakerNameEn": "Natsuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-hanano002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと～、失礼だよ。franさんのブランド\nもう随分前に、なくなっちゃったんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ that's rude. fran-san's brand\nwent out of business a long time ago!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6650735698,
      "endTime": 125.4980213008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "麗亜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rea",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_02-reia006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだっけ？\nすみませ～ん、私ってば、すっかり忘れてました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ is that so?\nI'm sorry‚ I completely forgot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7650623801,
      "endTime": 133.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
