      "text": "（マズいな、頼りにしてたmihoさんまでキレてる）\n（……いや、この人、そんなに頼りになったっけ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is bad. Even miho-san‚ who I was counting on‚ is angry.）\n（Wait‚ was she really that reliable in the first place?）",
        "id": ""
      },
