      "text": "あははははは、mihoも結局キレてんじゃん！\nもういい大人なのにね～、一番年食ってるのにね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha‚ miho's mad too!\nShe's a grown-up‚ the oldest one here‚ and she's still mad!",
        "id": ""
